{"tid":2233992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日TVB] 說謊的人要吞一千根針 咁說謊的公司呢？","createTime":"2020-10-07T13:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T16:57:38.000Z","uid":102331,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"508e63b996cf39a2735705aaa0ea5195edb635e6","tid":2233992,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">要收一千個嬲啊! （最少）<br />\n無口齒嘅公司 大家仲會唔會用？我就唔會囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<p class=\"center\">【每日任務@ 7 Oct】<br />\n💎 耀才證券 💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bsgroup1428/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbsgroup1428%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=7c23689d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bsgroup1428/</a></p><p class=\"center\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120734847_182448016804911_3345902902415524954_n.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=rbjbHMZQBCQAX_f8P6A&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-syd2-1.xx&amp;oh=26171df62c92d66678b0f8136e9a7ce4&amp;oe=5FA517A4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-syd2-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120734847_182448016804911_3345902902415524954_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DrbjbHMZQBCQAX_f8P6A%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-syd2-1.xx%26oh%3D26171df62c92d66678b0f8136e9a7ce4%26oe%3D5FA517A4&h=35ca7614&s={SIZE}\" /></p><br />\n-<br />\n😡1.派嬲 💬2.留言 🙅🏻♀3.轉用致富 👍🏻4.互Like留言<br />\n-<br />\n耀才證券上年呃人話唔會再喺TVB賣廣告，呃咗13K Likes，但今年新年就即刻反口落返廣告，仲話「大家都要搵兩餐」。DLLM做證券做到你咁無誠信？大家一於轉用致富證券！<br />\n-<br />\n（有代替有代替！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n上年有謠傳致富證券唔畀人參與「八&middot;五罷工」，董事郭家安聽到就即刻上連登post staff card辟謠，表明唔會炒罷工嘅同事，仲話自己都有請到假，由嗰陣起，佢就長駐連登，甚至做埋CS解答連登巴絲嘅疑問，咁好服務態度你話邊度搵？<br />\n-<br />\n💛 替代建議：致富證券<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397373</a><br />\n<br />\n留言template：<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">無綫電視立場偏頗，新聞部扭曲事實、管理層打壓良心員工、編劇為執政者鷹犬洗刷污名，但 貴公司仍然選擇助紂為虐，本人知道廣告商有選擇宣傳渠道的自由與權利，但 貴公司出爾反爾、欺騙投資者，違反了不會再於無綫電視投放廣告的承諾，行為令人不齒，故此本人將會抵制 貴公司，並呼籲大眾轉用良心公司致富證券。</span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"red\">【‼TVB 廣告商抵制名單‼】</span><br />\n詳細名單：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/TVBAdData\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FTVBAdData&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=e0091494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/TVBAdData</a> 👈🏻<br />\n重點名單：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/LeafletColorv21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FLeafletColorv21&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=10cfd90c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/LeafletColorv21</a> 👈🏻</p></span><br />\n<br />\ncr. 抵制tvb戰線 - 鍵盤救港 @sayno4tvb facebook"},{"pid":"36bc9d6c05190396c51c828d936cb5f17422be27","tid":2233992,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:55:50.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"702a7787987ddbcc261f087469336fe3d859739e","tid":2233992,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"438ccc507d9e832c805e28a7196f1a7745850b56","tid":2233992,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4ff8aa3fab41b91a2f1768f6f99bb6e0356cdf2b","tid":2233992,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:56:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"992a747c932f82df3a6f1bc647ff4b1ba4241925","tid":2233992,"uid":102331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:56:30.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"1e22e1d0a8f3996446af25bc400f2ef2f4f61745","tid":2233992,"uid":27122,"lik